LUNCHEON
SERVICE
We are pleased to offer a variety of dining options tailored to
suit your inflight schedule. You may select our traditional luncheon
service, our Lighter Fare entree service, which allows you to create
your own entree from the Salad Cart, or our Dine Upon Request™
option, a complete meal presented all at once, shortly after take-off
or later in the flight, whenever you prefer. If you should choose
our Dine Upon Request option and wish to dine as soon
as possible, please notify your flight attendant.
APPETIZERS
To START
Warm mixed Nuts or fresh Vegetables and Dip
to accompany your preferred Cocktail or Beverage
THE SALAD CART
Seasonal mixed Greens
with Coconut Garlic Herb Dressing or spicy Thai Vinaigrette
Lobster Tail and Claw with lemon wedges
Thai Chicken
Thai Pasta Salad
BREAD BASKET
Warm Sourdough and Seven-Grain Rolls
CONDIMENT TRAY
Help yourself to an assortment of different seasonings
that allows you to customize the flavors of your entree.
A-1 Steak Sauce • Hot Sauce • Salt Free Seasoning • Lemon Pepper
ENTREES
BALSAMIC MARINADE CHICKEN
Grilled Chicken with a Balsamic Marinade
presented with Red Onion and Fennel Saute
on a bed of Tomato Rice Pilaf
MEDITERRANEAN PASTA
Penne Pasta in a natural Balsamic Broth,
tossed with Spinach, Capers, Kalamata Olives
and Red Bell Peppers, garnished with fresh Goat Cheese
PASTRAMI SANDWICH
A hot Pastrami Sandwich served on Rye Bread
with roasted Garlic, Shallot and Dijon Mustard Potato Salad
SMOKED SALMON WITH MIXED GREENS
Peppered Smoked Salmon chilled and presented on a bed of mixed Greens,
offered with grilled Onions, marinated Carrots and a Chervil Cream Sauce
LIGHTER FARE
If you wish to create your own entree
from the Salad Cart, you may do so.
Dessert and Cordials will immediately follow your meal.
DINE UPON REQUESTSM
In an effort to accommodate your individual preferences,
American Airlines is pleased to offer any of the entrees listed below
for your Dine Upon Request selection, complete with assorted fine Cheeses
and Apple Cheesecake, presented all at once,
at any time you wish during the flight.
Balsamic Marinade Chicken • Mediterranean Pasta
Pastrami Sandwich • Smoked Salmon with Mixed Greens
Please notify your flight attendant with your preferred time of dining
and we will be happy to accommodate your specific needs.
